                secretKeyRef:\r\n                  key: password\r\n                  name: database-schema-admin\r\n          image: \"{{ .Values.environment }}{{ .Values.application_name | replace \"-\" \"\" }}.azurecr.io/{{ .Values.application_name }}-flyway-with-test-data:{{ .Values.version }}\"\r\n          imagePullPolicy: Always\r\n          name: flyway-migration\r\n          volumeMounts:\r\n            - mountPath: /flyway/conf\r\n              name: flyway-config\r\n            - mountPath: /mnt/secrets-store\r\n              name: secrets-store-inline\r\n              readOnly: true\r\n      restartPolicy: Never\r\n      volumes:\r\n        - configMap:\r\n            name: {{ .Values.application_name }}-flyway-conf\r\n          name: flyway-config\r\n        - csi:\r\n            driver: secrets-store.csi.k8s.io\r\n            readOnly: true\r\n            volumeAttributes:\r\n              secretProviderClass: azure-kvname\r\n          name: secrets-store-inline\r\n```\r\n\r\n2. I install the release with the following command:\r\n\r\n```\r\nhelm upgrade --install db-migration-release db-migration \\\r\n    --namespace migration-namespace \\\r\n    --set version=1.0.0.0 \\\r\n    --set application_name=test \\\r\n    --set environment=test \\\r\n    --set change_cause=test \\\r\n    --wait --wait-for-jobs --cleanup-on-fail --timeout 7m10s\r\n````\r\n\r\n3. The migration runs to completion. The Job/Pod has status `Complete`.\r\n\r\n# Expected result\r\n\r\nThe helm release finishes successfully shortly after the Job completes.\r\n\r\n# Actual result\r\n\r\nThe helm release waits for the full timeout duration and finishes with failure due to timeout. Resources are not cleaned up after the failed release.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/helm/helm/issues/9584/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/helm/helm/issues/9584/timeline"